      <p class="text-[54px] text-[#EE7380] font-extrabold">Explore</p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4 text-left lg:w-[75%]">
        Track your own data to see where you are doing well and where you have
        more potential for growth. Access all our metrics to see where you stand
